<p>Wednesday 26/9/17<br/>Spent day with 26th Bn who are very pleased with stunt 2 Off Killed 3 W.<br/>Thursday 27/9/17<br/>Rode over to see Bas also had a talk with Hotchkiss the General's old groom.<br/>Friday 28/9/17<br/>Had letter from Doff &amp; also wrote to her. Dinner with 2nd Div farewell to A.D.Ms 28th Bn bombed &ndash; took over command.<br/>Saturday 29/9/17<br/>Pow-wow about new attack made all arrangements for move.<br/>Sunday 30/9/17<br/>Left by Car to reconnoitre front line near Zonnebeke [Belgium] returned &amp; rejoined 28th at Canal Area.</p>
